CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. 26 reads: "Who Will Be "Miss WILY"? you pick the winner...Greta Jean Leach, Pittsburgh, Announcement of the winner and the coronation of "Miss WILY" will take place at Warners Cinerama, 336 Fifth Ave., Tuesday Evening, November 27th."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Greta Jean Leach wearing dark short sleeve dress with bow and brooch at collar, posed in interior with light colored walls for "Miss WILY" contest
